$interpreted: Sanchez: Hmph! I smell fear!
Sanchez: This piece of trash is the Kingdom's lowliest servant. At best, he's a walking piece of property.
Sanchez: If I want to hit him, I'll hit him. If I want to kick him, I'll kick him.
Sophie: YOU...!
Hutchinson: Sophie, now's not the time...!
Hanbei: Do you want to end up just like your father!?
Elio: If he's really a Priest's servant, then we've no right to interfere.
Elio: The Desert Kingdom worships the Snake God, and a Priest is a powerful position. The High Priest even shares a table with the royal class...
Sanchez: That's correct～ You're quite knowledgeable, are you from around here?
Elio: Just something I learned at the Academy. You ought to go. Best not to keep your master waiting.
Sanchez: Hmm, this time you got lucky!
Sanchez: Rune! Let's go!
Sophie: ...Wait!
Sophie: Rune, don't lose hope. You'll see us again! I'll bet you my reputation I'll make you smile next time!
Rune: ..."Hope"...wha...what does that mean...?
Elio: Wahhh...!?
Disciple: Wahahah! Found you! You thought you'd get away! You got away yesterday, but not today!
Elio: Did I get away? So not all the Dracontines can use those strange Runes...?
Elio: (I'd better get out of here before they find me. They said something about the Desert Kingdom...)
Sophie: Elio, we're about to have dinner～
Elio: I can't. Thanks, Sophie but I've got to get going.
Sophie: Huh? Where are you going?
Elio: The Desert Kingdom. Thanks for taking care of me yesterday. Tomorrow morning I'll...
Sophie: Oh! So are we!
Elio: ...Eh?
Sophie: We're to perform in the Bazaar for a bit. We had already planned to make the next stop the Desert Kingdom.
Sophie: Isn't that right?
Hanbei: Hey, didn't you just say we're NOT doing that? You said you were sick of wandering around. We told you yesterday and you got all up...
Sophie: WELLLLL, since we've all got the same plan, it'd be best to team up. We can take care of each other on the road.
Elio: ...Might as well...
Sophie: Okay then! It's decided! Morgan's Marvelous Circus, let's pack up! Tomorrow we set out for the Desert Kingdom!
